<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8262053>
    dc:description "FIGURE 155. Oenopia sauzeti Mulsant: a, b. adult, dorsal view; c. head and pronotum; d. elytral punctation (enlarged); e. antenna; f, g. male genitalia: f. tegmen, ventral view; g. penis; h. spermatheca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8262053/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8262055>
    dc:description "FIGURE 156. Oenopia sauzeti Mulsant, life stages: a, b. eggs on silver fir; c. early stage larva; d. full grown larva; e. pupa; f. Oenopia mimica adult, misidentified as O. sauzeti (From the archives of the erstwhile Commonwealth Institute of Biological Control–Indian Station)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8262055/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8262061>
    dc:description "FIGURE 157. Oenopia sauzeti Mulsant, life stages: a. eggs; b–d. larva; e. pupa; f–h. adult." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8262061/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

